Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:44.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:50.56,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用でぎこちないほど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.56,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛しく始まるの？
