Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 還有一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 讓明治政府從初設走向了近代化..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂五條御誓文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便是明治政府的基本方針
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:29.42,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}盯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:33.08,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}盯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:33.08,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在看什麼書呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 那個人是不是很帥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去搭話看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好睏..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.71,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}盯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀 帥小夥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好酷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.21,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}盯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:44.72,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}盯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:46.84,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}盯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂搬家過來已經多少年啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是讀幼兒園的時候搬來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以已經十年以上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算像這樣基本每天面對面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒見阿砂提過女生的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 完全不知道他喜歡的女生類型
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底喜歡什麼樣的女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓大和的戀慕修成正果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要知道這點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 我進來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 總是進來之後才這麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這什麼打扮..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛洗好澡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在用功嗎？明明離考試還早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:05:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 讀書是每天的必修課哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 雖然有些突然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我想問你喜歡什麼樣的女性？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很突然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AKB的話你支持誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我對藝人不熟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼塞拉小姐和芙勞·寶你挑哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡通？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼唱歌的大姐姐和練體操的大姐姐你選哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,體操吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼小舞和小翠你選哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:32.15,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}注：日本兒童節目中角色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練體操的大姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼就這麼得出結論了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和同學是哪一種呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝..謝謝..謝謝..謝謝..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很難懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真好懂呢 喜歡的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要看得過去的誰都可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑嘻嘻討人喜歡的你都愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺很可愛的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 無論什麼時候來看都像屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這是男人的屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 是男人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼事到如今一直沒發覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都看了十多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 你有女朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:08.08,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}一邊看著屁股松樹一邊被問這個也是醉了..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊 你不是很受歡迎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:14.09,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}太近了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道就不想和女生交往看看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢..好懶..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懶得想交往後該做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒搞錯啊 想那些事應該很開心才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 有沒有長蛋蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼對女生沒興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又沒說過沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就是有興趣囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:48.92,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}所以說太近了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通有興趣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有苗頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:07:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 給你個忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果懶得應付女生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後少做那種受歡迎的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種舉動..我才沒有積極去做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 也要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是“是！”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是“是..”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一種基本句型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不需要目的語和補語
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只用主語和動詞就能組成完整句子的句型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別睡著了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種句型中使用的動詞被稱為完全自動詞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是大和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做好了薩赫蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我能送過去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條信息是怎麼回事..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺..多彩多姿的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.03,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,舉個例文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:10.91,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,I go
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.59,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我去 的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時都可以來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:13.87,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(254,389)}{\frz330}隨時都可以來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高興  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以叫你猛男同學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還蹦來蹦去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要叫你大和..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和同學是個好姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂當然也是好小夥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人好般配
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂..所以說..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊走 速度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我也要去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都別問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做你自己就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼跟什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 日安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是薩哈蛋糕麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:57.74,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}薩哈蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.91,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}薩赫蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼美味的巧克力蛋糕 我從來沒嚐到過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧你能吃下這麼多 會胖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會運動的所以沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃多動 那是相撲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相撲麼 過獎過獎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒在稱讚你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去買點喝的過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思 是我疏忽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝什麼？我順便買過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一起..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用不用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是阿砂 做得好自然..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂很帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也這麼想吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我和他三歲就認識了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他相處都有十多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢夥從以前就是個好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幼兒園的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在話劇裡扮演主角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演的是“哭泣的赤鬼”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:13.40,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}哭泣的赤鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:16.32,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}媽媽見面日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男當赤鬼最好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來當赤鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:23.95,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}哭泣的赤鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扮演青鬼的阿砂以他那與年齡不符的名演技
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓媽媽們哭成一片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我則有點賣蠢..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演赤鬼的孩子 好像很強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小學一年級的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:44.18,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}唔哇哇哇哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直憋著想去廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果在大掃除的時候尿褲子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:48.06,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(370,62)}慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:45.68,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(755,62)}噗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然阿砂哈哈大笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但笑完之後 我們一起把桶子裡的水倒在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣瞞過了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:13:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 遠足時我因為興奮過頭打翻了便當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂雖然也笑得很誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是把自己的便當分了一大半給我 是一大半哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一說起阿砂的好處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何都會把自己羞恥的過去公諸於眾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是決定好要支持他們倆麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂他喜歡練體操的大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好像對女性也頗有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也沒有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他還有什麼呢..該怎麼做才能幫他們..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才好像嚐到了巧克力之外的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 中獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放了一個特別的進去 你吃到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中獎了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 中獎了..是栗子餡的..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栗子..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 只是吃到特別的啦..誒嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 中獎了啊 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以再做給你吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 錢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用啦 我們一直都白吃你蛋糕的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 這種事不分清楚的話 我會心裡不舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題 這點和你很搭哦 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..請問..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還能繼續傳信息給你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想問蛋糕喜好的時候..之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 我懂的 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是站在你這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂的手郵地址也告訴她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 為什麼？話說可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以是可以啦..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音太大啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點..走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我會在這裡被鋼筋壓死所以不行麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當不了白馬王子麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便這樣 那孩子也得救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣..就可以了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事 要不是他我們早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼纜固定 動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 你..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我..還蠻有力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 你的血
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這點小傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有嗎？我印象中應該有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 我有帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像..我總是被你救呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男..猛男..猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你撞到電線桿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:20.66,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:21.91,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,563)}爆\N炸\N頭\N理\N髮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 卡住了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會死哦 就算是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥豬大猩猩~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔臉~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她今天的蛋糕 很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 要振作一點才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我決定要支持他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支持大和的戀情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 猛男同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的傷沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真的要感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我才要謝謝 蛋糕很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再做來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 所以呢 那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次見面的時候..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不叫砂川同學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想兩個人單獨見面..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 啊 可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 下個休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一樣在公園噴泉前可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼一想 我還沒好好聽到大和的心意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在和阿砂的幾次見面之中 她的心意也漸漸堅定了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於 要跟我傾訴對他的愛慕了麼
